{
  "stem": "13690.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, it was quite difficult even having possessions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How do you make a living?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to go to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to be somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have to earn some money to support my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't have my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to go on markets, so to say, and to earn a living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was waiting till after the high holidays and to make up my decision, what to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To follow, to go on the road what my brother and sister went, to Palestine, or what, actually, it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The day before the high holidays, we were still in our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were two Jewish families in the town that survived, that they came back and made their home in that town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody from that town came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very few from the 4,000 Jews survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have no boy or girl of my age that survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Quite difficult to make your home in that home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Regardless of saying, the night, or the day before the high holidays, not erev, a day before them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Used to say practically two days before the high holidays, on Rosh Hashanah, grenades were thrown into our house, destroying the house and destroying the other house, the two Jewish homes that the Jews survived.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That gave us indication, you're not wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I would know who threw the grenades, I would definitely try to prosecute him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I can tell you, rest assured, that they were Poles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no more Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we realize that this is not our place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the safest place was that the Jews tried to congregate or to live in areas in bigger towns.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
